cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper deals with learning forward and inverse models for robotics, specifically using deep neural networks for image generation and state estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also heavily relies on computer vision techniques, such as deep convolutional networks, which suggests cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the second most likely category. The use of deep learning models for both forward and inverse mapping also suggests cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as likely categories. Finally, the validation of the models on a real robotic system suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a possible category.
